# рџЊЌ EcolytixDecentralized environmental monitoring infrastructure powered by real-world IoT sensors and verified on Solana blockchain.---# рџљЂ OverviewEcolytix is a real-time environmental monitoring platform that combines:- IoT sensors- Artificial Intelligence- Blockchain verification- Real-time dashboardsThe system captures air quality data using physical sensors, processes the information through an AI analysis engine, and stores verifiable telemetry records on Solana Devnet.Our goal is to create transparent and tamper-proof environmental monitoring infrastructure for smart cities, industries, and public spaces.---# рџ§  Key Featuresвњ… Real-time air quality monitoringвњ… Physical IoT hardware integrationвњ… AI-powered environmental trend analysisвњ… Solana blockchain verificationвњ… Immutable telemetry recordsвњ… Real-time dashboard visualizationвњ… Modular and scalable architecture---# рџЏ—пёЏ Architecture```textMQ135 Sensor     в†“Arduino Uno     в†“ USB SerialPython Serial Bridge     в†“FastAPI Backend     в†“AI Analysis Engine     в†“Solana Devnet Memo Program     в†“SQLite Database     в†“Web Dashboard

