рџ§¬ AI Engine
The AI module analyzes historical environmental readings to identify:


Pollution spikes


Air quality improvement trends


Stable environmental conditions


The analysis engine compares historical averages against recent readings to generate real-time insights.

в›“пёЏ Blockchain Verification
Each environmental reading is written to Solana Devnet using the Memo Program.
This creates:


Verifiable telemetry


Immutable environmental records


Transparent monitoring history


Users can inspect every transaction directly on Solana Explorer.

